OL,7,FThe monitoring of sewage discharges
OL,8,Finto Scotland's rivers must be
OL,9,Fdramatically improved amid fears
OL,10,Fofficial figures are underestimating
OL,11,Fthe problem, conservationists have
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FData published by Scottish Water, the
OL,15,Fpublicly-owned company in charge of the
OL,16,Fnation's sewage system, shows that
OL,17,Fbetween 2017 and 2021, sewage has
OL,18,Foverflowed directly into rivers and
OL,19,Fother water courses 54,289 times ` the
OL,20,Fequivalent of almost 30 times per day.
OL,3,CLack of monitoring of sewage flowing
OL,4,Cinto Scottish rivers is 'masking extent
OL,5,Cof the problem'
